      • OverrideConfigService

        public OverrideConfigService(java.util.Properties overrides,
                             AppContext c)
        Constructs a new OverrideConfigService that will return properties specified in overrides if they are present. overrides does not contain the requested property, parent will be used to fetch the requested property.
        Parameters:
        overrides - a collection of properties that will override properties stored in parent
        c - AppContext
